To visualize the test add following line of code to package.json and then in test:
--env=jsdom --verbose

so it should be like this:
"test": "react-scripts test --env=jsdom --verbose",

then install https://spaceship-prompt.sh/ with homebrew


install json-server from npm package:
sudo npm install -g json-server
Yoy can either run this line directly in terminal or add it to the package.json file using 
"server": "json-server --watch db.json --port 3010",

to watch json:
json-server --watch db.json --port 3010

to have a good visual experience of json files add JSON Viewer pro to google chrome
